msgid "Cache status checker automatically fires up whenever the status shows broken — it re-checks every 15 seconds for up to 3 minutes and stops the moment cache is active, so recovery shows up within 15 seconds of Batcache rebuilding. Once the cache status stays broken over 4 minutes it's likely that cache is broken due to cookie interference."
msgstr "Cache status checker automatically fires up whenever the status shows broken — it re-checks every 15 seconds for up to 3 minutes and stops the moment cache is active, so recovery shows up within 15 seconds of Batcache rebuilding. Once the cache status stays broken over 4 minutes it's likely that cache is broken due to cookie interference."

